        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 15-17 Etna Street, Brighton MA 02135 - Unit #15 ~ NO BROKER FEE! ~ ~ Less than 10-minute walk to Boston Landing Commuter Rail Stop ~ Available AUGUST 1st Bi-level 4-bed / 2-bath with off-street parking Property Features: - Spacious approx. 1,700-SF unit of living space on two upper levels - Sunny living room and common area for dining room on main floor - 1 bedroom on main floor, 3 bedrooms on 3rd floor - 2 full bathrooms, one on each floor - Stainless appliances (gas stove, fridge, and dishwasher) - Laundry in unit off kitchen, FREE! (not coin operated) - Private rear deck off kitchen - Off-street parking for up to 4 cars BUT shared with lower unit Utilities: - Tenants pay for gas, electricity, cable/wifi - Water/sewer included Deposits: - First month, Last Month & One Month Security Deposit",
