        "mainpic": "991d2449-ddd1-452e-9569-09a58cd923c4",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post $4,100/month · Available September 1 · Rental by owner — No broker fee - 2 bedrooms + dedicated office (flex 3rd bedroom with window and closet), 2 full baths - 1,334 sq ft, first floor of an owner-maintained three-family - Private backyard with lawn and patio — yours alone - In-unit washer/dryer included - Central air, hardwood and tile throughout - .2 mi to Lechmere (Green Line), 0.7 mi to Kendall/MIT (Red Line) - one year lease (first month rent / last month / one month security deposit) The Space Large, well-laid-out condo with a real living room and separate dining room, big windows, and excellent natural light. The primary bedroom is huge, with a skylight and en suite full bath. The second bedroom is a comfortable mid-size room overlooking the green backyard. The third room is an official bedroom, with a window and closet. It is smaller, and works well as a home office or single bedroom (fits a twin bed). Updated kitchen: stainless steel appliances, cherry cabinets, granite counters, dishwasher, disposal. The private backyard is a standout — quiet lawn and patio just for this unit, rare for East Cambridge. Location Quiet residential street in East Cambridge, minutes from Kendall Square, MIT, and the shops and restaurants of Cambridge Street. Easy walks: 0.2 mi to Lechmere MBTA (Green Line), 0.7 mi to Kendall MBTA and MIT Sloan (Red Line). On street parking. Parking is easy to find in this area.",
