        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Beautiful, bright top-floor brownstone apartment available in the South End, just steps from Boston Medical Center and the neighborhood’s restaurants, cafes, parks, and public transportation, available September 1st. This spacious apartment blends classic brownstone character with modern upgrades. It features two sizable bedrooms plus a separate office with custom built-ins, making it ideal for working from home. The large living room has an open layout that flows into a full dining area. The updated galley kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, ample storage, exposed brick, under-cabinet lighting, and a wine fridge. Additional features include: High ceilings Expansive windows with great natural light Hardwood floors throughout Two-zone mini-split central air / heating Large private composite rear deck Beautiful views of the Prudential and Hancock towers Well-maintained building The oversized rear deck is perfect for relaxing or hosting, with beautiful city views.",
