        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post NEWLY RENOVATED 2 bedroom apartment in AWESOME DANVERS NEIGHBORHOOD. Hot water included, you are responsible for electric. The apartment was recently renovated, including stainless appliances, fresh paint, doors, fully remodeled kitchen and bathroom in and new flooring. It features an open concept kitchen, living room and eating area! There are plenty of cabinets in the kitchen which is an open concept. New Floors feature in the main open area and the bedrooms. This unit features separate entrance to make it feel private and there is a HUGE yard with reserved parking in driveway for your vehicles (2). This apartment is on the third level, in a well maintained house in a VERY desirable location of Danvers. While the apartment is on a quiet street it is within 2 miles of Route 128 and route 1, 2 miles to the Liberty Tree Mall, 3 miles to the Northshore Mall and is also in walking distance to several eateries and downtown shopping. There is off-street parking in the driveway. The unit is available now. Please email me for address and time to see unit. LARGE clean storage area is available in basement! Washer/Dryer in common clean basement. Utilities included are Hot Water and You pay for electric which in Danvers is supplied by town at a discount!",
