        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Rare opportunity for an affordable Two Bedroom Apartment For Rent in the heart of Belmont's thriving Cushing Village on Trapelo Road. Located on the 3rd floor, this comfortable three room, two bedroom and one bath condo features a large balcony to optimize the unit's space, light and hardwood floors. Spacious kitchen. This property gives you the opportunity to create your ideal home. Across the street the 73 express bus to Mt. Auburn Hospital, Mclean Hospital, Harvard Square Red Line T in 10 minutes and gives easy access to greater Boston and Cambridge. Close to the Commuter Rail to Boston, Route 2 and Belmont Center. Heat and Hot Water Included in the rent. Parking space available for additional fee. Rent is $2,795 a month, 3rd person for $95 extra a month. To watch video (Copy, Paste link) https://youtu.be/RtCD0hh919E?feature=shared Available September 1, Easy to Show, Call / Text Nick 617-699-0533",
