        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post For one person only - Beautiful sun soaked large apartment on second floor of lovely home, quiet neighborhood, wonderful neighbors below. 2 bedrooms, kitchen, dining room, and huge living room, 3 season sunroom, lots of windows and natural light. Huge covered front porch. Convenient location in north east Watertown on Belmont/Cambridge line, easy walk to grove street friend and fresh pond Quiet friendly neighborhood with mix of older folks, families, and working professionals. One off street parking spot for winter parking ban months No pets, no smoking or any kind indoors or outdoors Washer dryer potentially available for purchase Gas stove, fridge, dishwasher included 12 month lease starting Aug 1. No broker fee, no security deposit. I’ve lived here for 2 years, only leaving to move in with my partner. :) If interested, please reply with a bit about yourself and what you’re looking for!",
