        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post PROPERTY INFO ID: 268556872 Rent: $2,400 / Month Beds: 1 Bath: 1 Available Date: 08/01/2026 Pet: Cats & Small Dogs Only Rent Includes:: Heat, Hot Water Parking:: off-street parking This is a really nice unit located on the first floor of a four unit building. There is an assigned parking spot included with the rent, that is located near the entrance of the unit. There is a patio right outside the kitchen door where you can hang out and grill. The kitchen is equipped with plenty of cabinets, a gas stove, a refrigeraotr, and a dishwasher. There is also room for a small table. The living room and bedroom are both good sized. The hardwood floors were recently sanded and poly'd. New tile flooring and a vanity were installed in the bathroom. There is free laundry in the basement as well as a storage unit. Rent includes heat and hot water. A cat or small dog is ok with approval from the condo association. Unit is avaialable for an 8/1/26 lease start date. Owner requires 1st month's rent and a 1 month security deposit. There is no broker fee. Please come take a look soon before this unit gets rented. Thanks. Thanks, Steve Steve Sapontzis 617-590-6508(c) Uptown Realty",
