        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post PROPERTY INFO ID: 110175682 Rent: $3,650 / Month Beds: 2 Bath: 1 Available Date: 09/01/2026 Pet: Pet Friendly Rent Includes:: Garbage, Heat, Hot Water, Water Parking:: off-street parking This is a nice place that is just a short walk to Coolidge Corner, Trader Joe's, shops, and restaurants. This 3rd floor apartment has great light and nice hardwood floors. Heat and hot water are included with the rent There is laundry in the building. The kitchen is eat in and even has a dishwasher. The bathroom is clean and tiled. There is pretty good closet space as well. The apartment also has a nice big living room and a small back porch(shared) to hang out on after a long day at the office. Small pets, including dogs, are ok with the owner. Available for a 9/1 lease start date. Pictures are from previous tenants. There is no month broker fee. Parking spots are available for $250 per month. Please call or e-mail to see this or other units. Nice Place * Great Location * Porch * Pet Friendly Brownstone - Brick Thanks, Steve Steve Sapontzis 617-590-6508(c) Uptown Realty",
