        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post A beautiful, gorgeous 2-bed, 1-bath, lightly furnished apartment on the first floor of a two-family house in Newton available immediately. Walking distance to Wholefood, Star Market, Elementary and High schools, dog park, tennis court, Commuter rail to downtown Boston, access to Highway 90. 15-minute drive to Cambridge and downtown Boston. 2-3 car parking spaces on the driveway for this unit. There is also a four bedroom apartment available on the second and third floor of the same house ($4000/month). There are two bedrooms on the third floor which make perfect home office spaces if you need separate working area at home. Rent includes water. You are responsible for electricity, gas and rental insurance. 6-month minimal lease, but longer leases are preferred. The house is operated by the owner and no broker fees. One month deposit required. Thank you!",
