        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Apartment Rental Experts - Porter Square Two baths * Mini-split AC * Laundry in Unit * Garage * Pets OK! Somerville / Porter Square / Davis Square Available: 9/1/2026 || Fee: No Fee || Reference: #181739 Apartment Summary Check out this top floor condo in a three family home steps from Porter Sq and Davis Sq. Amazing layout with formal living room + dining room and fully applianced open concept kitchen. Stack laundry is right off the kitchen. Three bedrooms with plenty of room and closet space. The primary bedroom has an en suite bath and multiple closets. The other two bedrooms have mini-split heat pump unis on the wall for AC + the landlord will supply additional window AC units if needed for other rooms. Storage is available in the basement, and one garage parking spot is included. Pets with excellent references are fine. Fantastic location barely two blocks from Porter Square and very close to Davis. You don't see places like this very often! (Reference #181739) Features Cats allowed. Large and small dogs allowed. 2 minute walk to Major Bus Routes. 5 minute walk to the T. Garage Parking. Washer in unit, Dryer in unit, Heat Pump, Forced Hot Air. Three-Family structure, Wood Frame architecture, on the 3 floor, 1234 square feet. Apartment Details Kitchen: Open Concept. Separate dining room. Appliances include: Refrigerator, Electric Stove, Dishwasher, Garbage Disposal, Microwave, Pantry. Bath: 2 Bedrooms: 3 Reference: #181739 Fee: No Fee Available: September 01, 2026 Location: Somerville/Porter Square Contact Information Agent: Ben Keddy Call: 781-645-8736 Please mention reference # 181739 * Availability, fee and monthly rent are subject to change. Please call to verify details. ** Pictures are of model unit, and furnished appliances may vary. HUD: Equal Housing Opportunity",
