        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Apartment Rental Experts - Porter Square Absolutely mint - gut renovation - extra large studio Somerville / Porter Square / Available: 9/1/2026 || Fee: No Fee || Reference: #139119 Features Cats allowed. Large and small dogs allowed. Washer in unit, Dryer in unit, Central. Inquire about Off Street Parking. 1 minute walk to Major Bus Routes. 6 minute walk to the T. Two-Family structure, Wood Frame architecture, on the 1st floor. Apartment Summary Killer renovation with stainless steel appliances and cool modern peninsula in kitchen area. The living area and kitchen are one open room and the living area apart from kitchen is not large. That's why I say it is sort of almost an extra large, ++ studio. But \"1 bedroom efficiency\" is the most apt phrase. Bedroom is very good sized. So close to the T it is shocking. (Reference #139119) Apartment Details Reference: #139119 Location: Somerville/Porter Square Available: September 01, 2026 Fee: No Fee Bath: 1 Bedrooms: Studio + Kitchen: Open Concept. Appliances include: Refrigerator, Natural Gas Stove, Dishwasher, Microwave. Contact Information Agent: Ben Keddy Call: 781-645-8736 Please mention reference # 139119 * Availability, fee and monthly rent are subject to change. Please call to verify details. ** Pictures are of model unit, and furnished appliances may vary. HUD: Equal Housing Opportunity",
