        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 2 Bedrooms | 1 Bathroom | 1,014 Sq Ft Beautifully renovated top-floor condo in a classic brownstone, ideally located just 100 yards from the heart of Coolidge Corner and directly across from St. Mark's Park. This bright and spacious 1,014 sq ft home offers the perfect combination of charm, comfort, and convenience in a peaceful setting. Monthly Rent: $3,900/month (Heat/Water/Trash included) Available: September 1, 2026 Features: - Renovated top-floor unit in a well-maintained brownstone - 2 spacious bedrooms and 1 full bathroom - 1,014 sq ft of living space - Hardwood and tile flooring throughout - Modern kitchen with dishwasher, range/oven, refrigerator, and freezer - In-unit washer and dryer - Heat/Water/Trash included - Private locked storage unit included - 1 off-street tandem parking space included - Renter's insurance required Location Highlights: - Just 0.3 mile from the heart of Coolidge Corner - Directly across from St. Mark's Park - Walking distance to the Green Line (Summit Avenue Station) : 0.2 mile - Quiet, park-side location with no major road in front of the building - Restaurants, cafés, grocery stores, and everyday conveniences are all within walking distance This top-floor unit is exceptionally quiet, offering a peaceful retreat while being just steps from everything Coolidge Corner has to offer. Pets: Pets may be considered. Don't miss this opportunity to live in one of Brookline's most sought-after neighborhoods with included heat, parking, private storage, and outstanding walkability. Available for move-in starting September 1, 2026. Contact for more information or to schedule a showing.",
