        "geocode_query": "clary street, cambridge",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Bright & Spacious 3BR in Prime Inman Square Location Parking Included Enjoy this large, sun-filled 3-bedroom, 1 bath apartment situated on a quiet street in the highly sought-after Inman Square neighborhood. Conveniently located within walking distance to Harvard Square, MIT, the new Union Square T stop and an array of top restaurants, cafes, and shops. The apartment features a generous living room perfect for relaxing or entertaining, along with a newly renovated kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher, gas stove, and full-size refrigerator. Modern cabinetry and granite countertops complete the space. Additional highlights include: Recently renovated bathroom Beautifully refinished hardwood floors throughout Abundant natural light 1 off-street parking space included On-site washer and dryer in the basement A rare opportunity to live in one of Cambridge's most desirable locations with both comfort and convenience.",
        "phone": "",
