        "mainpic": "e4316a0f-438d-485c-8584-f8bc589e14ac",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post PROPERTY INFO ID: 440831424 Rent: $2,050 / Month Beds: 0 Bath: 1 Available Date: 09/01/2026 Pet: Cats Allowed Rent Includes:: Heat, Hot Water Parking:: street parking *No Broker's Fee!* Available for Sept 1st! (Cleaned and painted between tenants) The move-in costs are only First & Last Month's rent to move-in Sun Soaked! Gorgeous and Fully Remodeled Studio apartment on the corner of Strathmore and Orkney Road, situated on the Brighton/Brookline border. Located in the heart of the Cleveland Circle neighborhood of Brighton, just steps from Brookline. The C-Line is around the corner on Beacon St, and it's only 6-7 minutes walking distance to B or D Lines. There is a new Butterfly Mx Video intercom system providing a video feed to your mobile device, as well as keyless entry for the front door. This renovated unit features hardwood flooring throughout, a foyer, a renovated galley kitchen with white cabinets, granite counters, and stainless-steel appliances, including a dishwasher, microwave, and stove. There is a sunny, spacious living area at the corner of the building with 5 windows, a fully remodeled bathroom, and a large walk-in closet. The rent includes heat and hot/cold water, and there are on-site laundry facilities and indoor bike storage. - No Broker's Fee! - Professionally Managed - Located on the 3rd floor (Walkup plus 2 flights of stairs, no elevator) - Butterfly Mx Video intercom system (Video feed to your mobile device) - Conveniently located near the B, C, and D Lines (*See Public Transit Below*) - Steps from the C-Line on Beacon St - Right by the Chestnut Hill Reservoir - Cat-Friendly - Indoor bike storage - Laundry facilities on-site (Coin or Mobile Pay) - Fitness Center on-site (Free for Residents) - Free on-street parking with and without a residential permit - Includes the supply of heat and hot/cold water. Public Transit - C-Line at Englewood Station is just a 1-minute walk - 6-minutes walking distance to the D-Line at Reservoir Station - 6-minutes walking distance to the B-Line at Chestnut Hill Ave - 4-minutes walking distance to the 51 & 86 Bus Stop null",
