        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post AVAILABLE SEPTEMBER 1ST (9/1/2026) Located near Tufts University and Davis Square, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath first-floor apartment offers generous living space, modern finishes, and a prime location. The updated kitchen features white granite countertops, stainless-steel appliances, and modern cabinetry, creating a clean and contemporary feel. A separate living room provides comfortable, defined living space, and the bathrooms are finished with sleek, modern tilework. Enjoy outdoor space with access to a backyard, perfect for fresh air and relaxation. Additional conveniences include coin-op laundry in the basement. Parking options include street parking with City permit, plus garage parking available for rent. Pet Policy: Pets are welcome for $75 per month, per pet. Highlights: 4 bedrooms / 2.5 bathrooms. First-floor unit. Modern kitchen with white granite counters and stainless-steel appliances. Separate living room. Modern tiled bathrooms. Backyard access. Coin-op laundry in basement. Street parking (City permit). Garage parking available for rent. Prime location. Pet-friendly ($75/month per pet).",
