        "locality": "Cambridge",
        "geocode_query": "western, Cambridge",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Beautiful 2 bedroom apartment for rent near Charles River/Central Sq Cambridge Great Apartment • Large apartment (~1200 square feet) • 10 foot ceilings and lots of light • New hardwood floors • 2 bedrooms, but can be easily converted to 3 bedrooms if desired. • Living room, dining room, kitchen, bathroom, walk-in closet, storage including pantry closet, and additional storage downstairs • Kitchen island, granite countertops, and new appliances (Kitchenaid fridge, Bosch dishwasher, LG stove and microwave) • Central A/C and central heat. • Huge backyard and private back deck. Rare outdoor space in Cambridge! • Free laundry (washer and dryer) downstairs. • 2 car parking available for small fee. • Cats OK. Can include some furniture if needed. Convenient Location • Extremely convenient location, a quick 5-minute walk to the Red line T. One stop to Harvard or Kendall. • 5-minute walk to Central Square, 15-minute walk to Harvard Square, 25-min walk to Kendall Square (MIT). • Easy 8-min driving commute into Boston. • 6-minute walk to the beautiful Charles River, and Memorial Drive (which is closed for biking and pedestrians on Sundays) • Convenient to H-Mart (7-min walk), Target (7-min walk), Whole Foods (9-min walk), and Trader Joes (13-mins). • Close to many restaurants, coffee shops, bars, and shopping, as well as parks, tennis courts, and playgrounds. • Great for students or young professionals. 15-min walk to Harvard Business School. Asking 3300$ per month. Includes water/sewer. Flexible move-in date, ideally Sept 1. One year lease. First month's rent and one month security deposit for move in. No fee. Credit and background check to be performed. Please email me with an introduction about yourself, preferred move-in date, and your phone number. I will reach out to you to schedule a showing. Thanks!",
        "phone": "",
        "image_urls": [
