        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post PROPERTY INFO ID: 2426474 Rent: $2,495 / Month Beds: 1 Bath: 1 Available Date: 07/01/2026 Pet: Cats Only Rent Includes:: Garbage, Heat, Hot Water, Water Parking:: street parking This unit has just been totally renovated! It's located on the 3rd floor of a professional/graduate student building in the heart of Packard's Corner. Everything in the kitchen and the bathroom is brand new. The kitchen comes equipped with brand new stainless steel appliances that include a dishwasher, gas stove, refrigerator and a built in microwave. New cabinets have just been installed. They all have soft close doors and drawers. There are really nice Quartz countertops and subway tiles in the kitchen. There are a few exposed brick walls in the kitchen. The bathroom has marble tiles on the floor and subway tiles on the walls. A new vanity, medicine, cabinet, and toilet were just installed. All of the hardwood floors have been sanded and poly'd. Rent includes heat, hot water, and cold water. There are 4 washers and 4 dryers in the building as well. The property manager is on site. The property manager and Superintendent are on call 24 hours a day. Cats are ok(no extra charge). The T stop is just a few steps away from the main entrance. Star Market, Super 88, Clear Flour Bakery, and a lot of restaurants and shops are a short walk away. The Owner requires 1st month's rent and 1 month security deposit. There is no broker fee! Available for an immediate or July 15th lease start date. Pictures were taken just before the current tenants moved in. Please call or email to set up a viewing. Thank you. Nice Brick Building in Packard's Corner. Property is in Brookline and Allston. International students are accepted. Great location. Thank You! FEATURES Elevator Featured High Ceiling Internet On-Site Super Thanks, Steve Steve Sapontzis 617-590-6508(c) Uptown Realty",
