        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Apartment Rental Experts - Porter Square Davis Sq - Renovated 3BR, 1.5 bath - Parking - Modern Kitchen Cambridge / Davis Square / Porter Square Available: 9/1/2026 || Fee: No Fee || Reference: #141615 Apartment Details Available: September 01, 2026 Bedrooms: 3 Reference: #141615 Fee: No Fee Kitchen: Eat in Kitchen. Separate dining room. Appliances include: Refrigerator, Stove, Dishwasher, Garbage Disposal. Bath: 1.5 Location: Cambridge/Davis Square Features Washer in unit, Dryer in unit. Two-Family structure, Wood Frame architecture, on the 2nd floor. Off Street Parking Available. 5 minute walk to the T. Apartment Summary Located in the Davis Square area of Somerville. Nicely renovated 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath apartment with gleaming hardwood floors throughout, living and formal dining rooms. Modern eat-in kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, dishwasher and disposal. Laundry in the unit, storage is in the basement and 1 tandem off street parking spot is included. Location is unbeatable, close to Davis and Porter Square. (Reference #141615) Contact Information Agent: Ben Keddy Call: 781-645-8736 Please mention reference # 141615 * Availability, fee and monthly rent are subject to change. Please call to verify details. ** Pictures are of model unit, and furnished appliances may vary. HUD: Equal Housing Opportunity",
