        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post PROPERTY INFO ID: 367740178 Rent: $1,700 / Month Beds: 0 Bath: 1 Available Date: 07/01/2026 Pet: Cats Only Rent Includes:: Garbage, Heat, Hot Water, Water Parking:: street parking NEW BATHROOM! Freshly painted studio in Packard's Corner. NO FEE! Nice garden level unit that was recently renovated. The entire bathroom was done over. There are beautiful porcelain tiles on the floor and shiny white subway tiles in the shower. New carpeting was installed a few years ago. The entire unit was painted. Rent includes heat, hot water, and cold water. Located on the garden level in a clean building in the heart of Packard's Corner in Allston(on the Brookline line). It's on the T and very close to Shaw's, Super 88, Clear Flour Bakery, and lots of local restaurants. There are 4 washing machines and 4 dryers right down the hallway. Cats are ok. Available now or 8/1/26! A virtual tour and in person tours are available on request. Owner requires good credit, 1st months rent, and a 1 month security deposit. There is no broker fee. Pictures were taken just before the current tenant moved in. Please give us a call or send an email if you have any questions or want to see the apartment. Thank You! Nice Brick Building in Packard's Corner. Property is in Brookline and Allston. International students are accepted. Great location. Thank You! FEATURES Elevator Featured High Ceiling Internet Thanks, Steve Steve Sapontzis 617-590-6508(c) Uptown Realty",
